{
  "$schema": "https://www.designtokens.org/schemas/2025.10/format.json",
  "$description": "Hearth-Story is a warm humanist system for nonprofits, community groups and social enterprises — the light of a room lit by a low fire. A deep ember primary glows against warm oat paper and sand surfaces while charred-walnut ink carries long, readable stories. Fraunces serif sets emotional display headlines and Source Sans keeps body copy human and calm. The bright ember accent never touches text; it survives only as glow, brushed underlines and spark marks. The signature is a hand-brushed ember signoff and a before-and-after story turn that warms cool grief into firelight. Tactile, restrained, never corporate.",
